name: Margaux Lange Ring
description:
These unique and eye catching ring feature Barbie doll eye with resin surround. Lovely and subtle.

Entirely hand-fabricated from start to finish, jewelry made by Margaux Lange, using salvaged Barbie doll parts, sterling silver and hand-pigmented resins.

Adjustable ring band fits approximately size 6 - 8. Artist signature on back.

Entirely handmade by Margaux Lange.

name: Margaux Lange Brown Eye Necklace
description:
Barbie Doll Eye Necklace with Pearl Drop features a salvaged Barbie doll eye, encased in a hand-fabricated sterling silver setting with hand hammered detailing. A single fresh water pearl drop, a sweet feminine detail, serves as a nod to Barbie's perfect pearly whites.

Pendant measures approximately 5/8" x 1 1/4" The necklace is on a 16" chain with lobster clasp closure, oxidized finishing and artist signature on the back.

Entirely hand-fabricated from start to finish, jewelry made by yours truly, using salvaged Barbie doll parts and sterling silver.

name: Margaux Lange Barbie Smile Neckless
description:
This new pendant design is one part sweet, one part punk rock. Pink lip Barbie smile is surrounded by pigmented black resin which has subtle black on black recessed polka dots that shimmer when they catch the light. Black spinel gemstone drops polish off the design.

18" chain with a lobster clasp, oxidized sterling silver finishing. Pendant measures approximately 1.5" in diameter. Artist signature on back.
